OL,3,CThree arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter man dies in Tredegar
OL,6,FThree men have been arrested after a
OL,7,Fman died in Tredegar town centre.
OL,9,FGwent Police says "early enquiries
OL,10,Findicate that the victim, a 36-year
OL,11,Fold Tredegar man, was involved in a
OL,12,Fphysical altercation between Friday
OL,13,Fnight, from around 10pm, into the
OL,14,Fearly hours of Saturday morning,
OL,15,Faround 2am."
OL,17,FThree men, aged 18, 19, and 51, have
OL,18,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,19,Fand remain in police custody.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
