OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1773191769
OL,3,CThree arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter man dies in Tredegar
OL,6,FThe family of the victim is being
OL,7,Fsupported by specialist officers.
OL,9,FDetective Chief Inspector Robin Fuller
OL,10,Fsaid: "We are in the early stages of
OL,11,Fthis investigation, and I offer my
OL,12,Fthoughts to the family of the victim.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
