CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1773191769
OL,3,CThree arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter man dies in Tredegar
OL,6,F"We're working to establish the full
OL,7,Fcircumstances and are particularly
OL,8,Finterested in speaking to anyone who
OL,9,Fwas in the area of Castle Street,
OL,10,Fopposite the Castle Hotel and Jem's
OL,11,Fjewellery, between 1am-2am on Saturday
OL,12,Fmorning. If you have dash cam footage
OL,13,Fthis could also help our investigation
OL,14,Fso please get in touch.
OL,16,F"Our officers remain in the Tredegar
OL,17,Farea as they continue to gather
OL,18,Fevidence and if you have any questions
OL,19,For information, then please do speak
OL,20,Fto them."
